Business-Logic version 0.01
===========================

Created by Benjamin Harnett, this module has some useful functions for any e-commerce website. These include shopping cart logic, logic for calculating available inventory, discounts, etc.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Should be relatively dependency free.

